text: Bad Hole Cave is an impressively large rising cave in the Cockpit Country of Jamaica. This is a limestone Karst region that is very rich in caves. ==See also== *List of Caves in Jamaica *Jamaican Caves Organisation ==External links== *Aerial view. *Photos: *Bad Hole Cave - Jamaican Caves Organisation ==References== Category:Caves of Jamaica Category:Geography of Trelawny Parish Category:Caves of the Caribbean
